<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Vibe Air Guitar</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="./styles.css?v=22">
</head>
<body>
  <main class="app">
    <section class="stage">
      <div class="video-wrap fx-off">
        <video id="camera" autoplay muted playsinline></video>
        <div class="camera-fallback" id="cameraFallback">开启摄像头，摆 1-5 号手势开弹</div>
        <canvas id="handCanvas" aria-hidden="true"></canvas>
        <canvas id="faceCanvas" aria-hidden="true"></canvas>
        <div class="effects-layer" id="effectsLayer" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="gesture-badge">
          <span id="gestureName">未选择手势</span>
          <strong id="activeChord">--</strong>
          <em id="detectStatus">手势识别就绪，松手即停</em>
        </div>
        <div class="live-gesture-palette" id="liveGesturePalette"></div>
        <div class="beat-meter" id="beatMeter"></div>
        <div class="drum-touch-zone active" id="drumTouchZone" aria-label="手势触控鼓">🥁</div>
        <div class="theme-switch" id="themeSwitch" aria-label="主题切换">
          <button type="button" data-theme-choice="light" aria-label="亮色主题">☀️</button>
          <button type="button" data-theme-choice="dark" aria-label="暗色主题">🌙</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <aside class="controls">
      <header>
        <p>本地浏览器版</p>
        <h1>Vibe Air Guitar</h1>
      </header>

      <div class="panel">
        <div class="row">
          <button id="cameraBtn" class="secondary">开启摄像头识别</button>
          <button id="playBtn">开始伴奏</button>
        </div>
        <div class="row single">
          <button id="autoBtn" class="secondary">松手即停</button>
        </div>
        <label>
          BPM
          <input id="bpm" type="range" min="60" max="140" value="92">
          <span id="bpmValue">92</span>
        </label>
        <label>
          调性
          <select id="keySelect">
            <option value="C">C</option>
            <option value="C#">C#</option>
            <option value="D">D</option>
            <option value="D#">D#</option>
            <option value="E">E</option>
            <option value="F">F</option>
            <option value="F#">F#</option>
            <option value="G">G</option>
            <option value="G#">G#</option>
            <option value="A">A</option>
            <option value="A#">A#</option>
            <option value="B">B</option>
          </select>
          <span id="keyLabel">C调</span>
        </label>
        <label>
          音色
          <select id="instrumentSelect">
            <option value="guitar">吉他</option>
            <option value="electric">电吉他</option>
            <option value="piano">钢琴</option>
            <option value="tinbox">半岛铁盒</option>
            <option value="glassbell">玻璃铃</option>
            <option value="celeste">星光琴</option>
            <option value="violin">小提琴</option>
          </select>
        </label>
        <label>
          Capo
          <input id="capo" type="range" min="0" max="5" value="0">
          <span id="capoValue">0</span>
        </label>
      </div>

      <div class="panel chord-panel">
        <h2>和弦谱</h2>
        <textarea id="progressionInput" rows="2">C G Am F</textarea>
        <div class="chord-picker">
          <div class="chord-picker-head">
            <span>单个和弦快捷添加</span>
            <button id="clearProgressionBtn" class="clear-progression-btn" type="button" aria-label="清空和弦谱">×</button>
          </div>
          <div class="quick-chord-rows" id="quickChordRows"></div>
        </div>
        <label class="stacked-label preset-label">
          📋 预制和弦模板
          <select id="progressionPresetSelect"></select>
        </label>
        <div class="progression-strip" id="progressionStrip"></div>
        <p class="hint">输入真实和弦名，系统会反查应该摆几号国际数字手势。</p>
      </div>

      <div class="panel">
        <h2>节奏型</h2>
        <div class="rhythm-modules">
          <section class="rhythm-card">
            <h3>🥁 鼓节奏</h3>
            <label class="toggle-row"><input id="drumToggle" type="checkbox" checked> 鼓开关</label>
            <label class="stacked-label">
              鼓节奏型
              <select id="drumRhythmSelect"></select>
            </label>
          </section>
          <section class="rhythm-card">
            <h3>🎸 吉他弹奏</h3>
            <label class="stacked-label">
              吉他节奏型
              <select id="rhythmSelect"></select>
            </label>
            <div class="toggle-list">
              <label><input id="muteToggle" type="checkbox"> 闷音 x</label>
              <label><input id="spreadToggle" type="checkbox" checked> 扫弦 spread</label>
              <label><input id="randomToggle" type="checkbox" checked> <span id="humanizeLabel">💡 人性化演奏</span></label>
              <label><input id="drumTouchToggle" type="checkbox" checked> 🎛️ 手势触控鼓</label>
            </div>
            <label class="stacked-label">
              和弦切换延迟
              <input id="chordSwitchDelay" type="range" min="0" max="800" value="150" step="10">
              <span id="chordSwitchDelayValue">150ms</span>
            </label>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="panel">
        <h2>演奏方式</h2>
        <div class="segmented" id="patternButtons"></div>
        <div id="customMelodySection" class="custom-melody-section">
          <p class="hint">编辑自定义走向：先录入，再保存，循环时自动套用根音换算。</p>
          <div class="custom-string-grid" id="customStringButtons"></div>
          <div class="custom-progression-row">
            <div id="customProgressionDisplay" class="custom-progression-tags"></div>
            <span id="customRootHint" class="custom-root-hint">根音自适应已开启</span>
          </div>
          <div class="custom-actions">
            <button id="customEditBtn" class="secondary">编辑</button>
            <button id="customSaveBtn" class="secondary">保存</button>
            <button id="customClearBtn" class="secondary">清空</button>
          </div>
          <p class="hint" id="customMelodyHint">选择“自定义”演奏方式后，任何音色都可用自定义走向，根音弦自动随和弦变化。</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="panel compact binding-panel">
        <h2>当前手势绑定</h2>
        <div id="mappingText" class="gesture-binding-list"></div>
        <p class="hint">切换调性会重置手指绑定；手动选择后会立刻用于播放。</p>
        <p>手在镜头里才响；只识别 1-5，减少误触发。音色会跟随当前手势和弦实时切换。</p>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </main>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@mediapipe/camera_utils/camera_utils.js"></script>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@mediapipe/drawing_utils/drawing_utils.js"></script>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@mediapipe/hands/hands.js"></script>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@mediapipe/face_detection/face_detection.js"></script>
  <script src="./app.js?v=22"></script>
</body>
</html>
